description: Nothing beats freshly baked cinnamon rolls drizzled with a sticky cream cheese icing. Learn how to make your own from scratch with this easy recipe.
name: Cinnamon Scrolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake scrolls for 20 minutes or until risen and golden. Drizzle cream cheese mixture over scrolls, then serve.
